<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="aim-n">aim <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /eɪm/    美 /eɪm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>瞄准：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Alan <strong>took aim at</strong> the target.
艾伦瞄准了目标。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-goal">2.★ <strong>[C] 目标 (goal)；目的</strong></h4>
<p>sth you intend to do; a purpose：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>achieve</strong> / <strong>realize one’s aim</strong>
达到目的/实现目标</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>miss one’s aim
没打中目标；没达到目的</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>aim of</strong> this is to reduce air pollution. 
这样做的目的是减少空气污染。</p><footer> 译林⑦ – 4</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="take-aim-at">take aim at</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把目标对准…；把批评的矛头指向…</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="with-the-aim-of">with the aim of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>旨在；目的是：</strong>  </p></div>